																			<span class="SG_txtb">标签：</span>
																																<h3><a href="http://search.sina.com.cn/?c=blog&q=%C3%C0%D6%B8&by=tag" target="_blank">美指</a></h3>
																																<h3><a href="http://search.sina.com.cn/?c=blog&q=%C3%C0%C8%F0&by=tag" target="_blank">美瑞</a></h3>
																																<h3><a href="http://search.sina.com.cn/?c=blog&q=%C3%C0%C8%D5&by=tag" target="_blank">美日</a></h3>
																																<h3><a href="http://search.sina.com.cn/?c=blog&q=%C5%B7%C3%C0&by=tag" target="_blank">欧美</a></h3>
																												</td>
									<td class="blog_class">
																			<span class="SG_txtb">分类：</span>
										<a target="_blank" href="http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/articlelist_1374857440_4_1.html">外汇行情分析</a>
